snippet.textDisplay:
As much as I love Emma & I am sad at how much hate she gets, I hope she takes this as a lesson that she cannot put halfway effort into her videos. I’ve shot & edited many videos before I know it is difficult but many creators with fewer subscribers have incredible content. And I get she’s going for the relatable, messy bun, self deprecating teenager look but, honestly I would like to see more effort. She has an incredible zest about her that shouldn’t be wasted & upping the production value wouldn’t be a bad thing. I’m tired of the ‘I just woke up & I’m bored’ type of video concept. Something needs to change & hopefully she knows that.

I am not hating in any way. I love Emma & I hope she changes for the better! 💖
